{"tid":1176992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"危機升級：華為失落日本5G關鍵訂單","createTime":"2019-05-29T14:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T01:29:34.000Z","uid":32938,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9f40f9fb39094ad554c411d6046410cf201c29f5","tid":1176992,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，日本電訊商軟銀集團(SoftBank Group)宣布，選擇了諾基亞(Nokia Oyj)及愛立信(Ericsson AB)為5G網絡供應商，排除了長期供應商華為。 <br />\n<br />\n軟銀指出，諾基亞將是5G的戰略夥伴，愛立信則是無線接入網絡設備的供應商。由於之前4G是由華為聯同中興通訊奪得，意味着5G的「班底」已徹底更換。軟銀沒有作出進一步解釋。 <br />\n<br />\n日本專家稱，軟銀作出此決定後，預計同業Docomo及KDDI會跟隨，故料軟銀不會受到成本提升所影響。"},{"pid":"c4abede70ac88db66bff508c2f704366b28a61db","tid":1176992,"uid":43173,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:39:22.000Z","msg":"同你講一年後冇晒零件換你仲用唔用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65a0b95bc0922280bc8d41fe25cf0f1a31c7915","tid":1176992,"uid":207208,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1Lqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=fe164378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a>"},{"pid":"6668bc4720908bcd556f8c6db08920396d19a1a5","tid":1176992,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi